 *     solid-state, trapped ions, quantum dots, photonic,
 *     superconducting).
 *   - sangouard-rmp-83 — atomic-ensemble memories and the DLCZ
 *     family of protocols.
 *   - knaut-nature-2024 — SiV-centre nanophotonic memory operating
 *     in a deployed telecom fibre network.
 *   - pompili-science-2021 — three-node NV-centre repeater demo
 *     using on-chip memories.
